---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section slot="head">
    <title>Inmocredit - Contacto</title>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-xl pb-xl bg-surface-container-low">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-xl items-center">
      <div class="z-10">
        <span class="inline-block px-md py-xs bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed rounded-full font-label-md text-label-md mb-md">
          Contáctanos
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl md:text-headline-xl mb-md text-on-surface">
          Estamos listos para ayudarte en tus proyectos
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">
          ¿Tienes dudas sobre tu crédito hipotecario o buscas la asesoría para vender tu propiedad? Nuestro equipo de expertos está listo para asesorarte en cada paso.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative h-[400px] md:h-[500px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-outline-variant">
        <img
          alt="Inmocredit Office"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBs3kDZjcAm168esY2iSTNq-2SLYSMV8tt6-J6IBxDDROVOkIwE5MTrvbK4XFcfrvcXnH541LIez1XAApOAJiYsqxS5dLEpy9IvwqfGrnGsde_i1nVGim6fpB5tuTqtjo7LE8iOfMxJtB237g6AaKDc-BXHhWyIoi8tc7egniE2kAfxScuqfPXYhycKONvusdcbYXSlZwfiQgOhLUlFX76CJp-x9AAHmrqRzthpEl6UYtBVsGWdZyfcLh12Garq02g9dwcipQsMDV0"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-primary opacity-5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info and Form Section -->
  <section class="py-xl bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-xl">
        <!-- Sidebar: Contact Info -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-lg">
          <div class="bg-white p-lg rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-md mb-lg">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-surface-container-low flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-primary">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-xs">Visítanos</h3>
                <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                  Blvd. Los Próceres 24-69 Zona 10, Torre I, Nivel 10, Oficina 1002, Guatemala, Guatemala.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-md mb-lg">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-surface-container-low flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-primary">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">call</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-xs">Llámanos</h3>
                <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                  +502 5094-8707<br />
                  +502 2354-6196
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-md">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-surface-container-low flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-primary">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-xs">Escríbenos</h3>
                <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                  contacto@inmocredit.gt<br />
                  info@inmocredit.gt
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden h-64 border border-outline-variant shadow-sm grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">
            <img
              alt="Map of Guatemala City"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCalT6kAm1FFNxk12wZCdidZYRSneMqM91AZgsZ67yTWHioli6RMQnkK0Dy1mGJ3plDEgYUQQjaLvPdyEU01GLY9W2FSWZ_oUbCQO8CiH_-7eRwiNVU_A_zbBCv4QQ2iI2zIaaJGNwQ__3K0E4FTjaC-Tcf80ejwzLQhVqkrj_Qp6NboidNSY9KqT4P_P5tyTeXn7ITlPdeTui13wcsQUNmFSZ8oj6h-EPBSRR6ck4Bclaf-3RJ9Bxx4lpS4hZdryV4Jjr2UgbkW8s"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Main: Contact Form -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-lg md:p-xl rounded-xl border border-outline-variant">
            <div class="mb-lg">
              <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-sm">Envíanos un mensaje</h2>
              <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Completa el formulario y un asesor se pondrá en contacto contigo en menos de 24 horas.</p>
            </div>
            <form action="#" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-md">
              <div class="space-y-xs">
                <label class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface" for="first_name">Nombre</label>
                <input class="w-full px-md py-sm bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-container focus:border-primary-container outline-none transition-all" id="first_name" placeholder="Tu nombre" type="text" />
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-xs">
                <label class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface" for="last_name">Apellido</label>
                <input class="w-full px-md py-sm bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-container focus:border-primary-container outline-none transition-all" id="last_name" placeholder="Tu apellido" type="text" />
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-xs">
                <label class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface" for="email">Correo Electrónico</label>
                <input class="w-full px-md py-sm bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-container focus:border-primary-container outline-none transition-all" id="email" placeholder="correo@ejemplo.com" type="email" />
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-xs">
                <label class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface" for="phone">Teléfono</label>
                <input class="w-full px-md py-sm bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-container focus:border-primary-container outline-none transition-all" id="phone" placeholder="+502 0000-0000" type="tel" />
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-xs">
                <label class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface" for="message">Mensaje</label>
                <textarea class="w-full px-md py-sm bg-white border border-outline rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-container focus:border-primary-container outline-none transition-all resize-none" id="message" placeholder="¿En qué podemos ayudarte?" rows="5"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="md:col-span-2 pt-md">
                <button class="w-full md:w-auto bg-[#FF6B35] text-white px-xl py-md rounded-full font-label-md text-label-md hover:shadow-[0_8px_20px_-4px_rgba(255,107,53,0.4)] transition-all active:scale-95" type="submit">
                  Enviar Mensaje
                </button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Success Story / Trust Section -->
  <section class="py-xl bg-on-tertiary">
    <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center">
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-base mb-md">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-lg">Más de 500 familias ya confiaron en nosotros</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-lg">
        <div>
          <p class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-primary mb-xs">98%</p>
          <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant">Clientes Satisfechos</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-primary mb-xs">15+</p>
          <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant">Años de Experiencia</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-primary mb-xs">24h</p>
          <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant">Respuesta Promedio</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-primary mb-xs">Q50M</p>
          <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant">Créditos Gestionados</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
